    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Stance)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 22</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>All your unarmed attacks count as Kensoku: Iaiken attacks, with the same bonuses. You take a -2 penalty to attack rolls, and gain a +2 bonus to any rolls made to confirm critical hits with such attacks. Inflicting the dazed condition multiple times in a round does not extend its duration.</p>\n\n\n\n",
